  "detailed_description": "<h1>DOWNLOAD THE SUNDERFOLK FREE TRIAL</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the first four missions of Sunderfolk for free! Test your skills in tactical encounters, try out your preferred control style (phone app or mouse & keyboard), and begin your adventure with the full roster of unique heroes. Best of all, your progress carries over seamlessly when you purchase the full game.</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover game night with Sunderfolk, a tactical co-op RPG built to bring people together. Whether teaming up across the globe via online multiplayer with a mouse and keyboard or playing couch co-op with phones as controllers, Sunderfolk adapts to your group. It’s your party, your plan, and your story to tell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/3501c38302ef2a444b51ee44435feebf.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing with phone controls? Only the host needs to own the game! Friends join for free using the free Sunderfolk Controller app as their hand of cards, guidebook, and controller. Just scan a QR code on a shared screen to jump right in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/b7164d43f7826aea02ac1b1411efd91c.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/8d4c474bbaad30c6f20ff4329ec0f1fd.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/8d4c474bbaad30c6f20ff4329ec0f1fd.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/8d4c474bbaad30c6f20ff4329ec0f1fd.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you prefer a traditional PC experience you can team up with friends seamlessly through native online multiplayer. Control your heroes directly using full mouse and keyboard support, with your skill cards and stats integrated right on your screen (online multiplayer requires each player to own a copy of the game).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/54c6cf90381aef30c88b541e3159df59.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/c624907e6d5518481e8c8c5c58c72d9f.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/c624907e6d5518481e8c8c5c58c72d9f.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/c624907e6d5518481e8c8c5c58c72d9f.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start your campaign and take on challenging missions together. Use powerful skill cards, choose your turn order, and plan every move. Outsmart enemies, adapt your tactics, and face down epic bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/a96a9a4f65b3eef069befac6c18f0d42.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between battles, unwind in the charming village of Arden. Upgrade shops, discover gear, share hearty meals, and connect with locals—some of whom may spark something more than friendship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/65bb5a0f10d4057ba7e5041f1b807923.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e013d9338cba857b6373a6f.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e013d9338cba857b6373a6f.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e013d9338cba857b6373a6f.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The magic of gathering around the table, without the setup. Whether you're passing around snacks on the couch or strategizing over voice chat online, Sunderfolk brings friends and families together through thoughtful strategy and shared laughs. It’s game night exactly the way it should be.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rediscover game night with Sunderfolk, a tactical co-op RPG built to bring people together. Whether teaming up across the globe via online multiplayer with a mouse and keyboard or playing couch co-op with phones as controllers, Sunderfolk adapts to your group. It’s your party, your plan, and your story to tell.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/3501c38302ef2a444b51ee44435feebf.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/ac173716d77cbe99240b2038d5541f27.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Playing with phone controls? Only the host needs to own the game! Friends join for free using the free Sunderfolk Controller app as their hand of cards, guidebook, and controller. Just scan a QR code on a shared screen to jump right in.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/b7164d43f7826aea02ac1b1411efd91c.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/