><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/a96a9a4f65b3eef069befac6c18f0d42.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/96848c475c387cd088dd19293177c8f6.mp4?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between battles, unwind in the charming village of Arden. Upgrade shops, discover gear, share hearty meals, and connect with locals—some of whom may spark something more than friendship.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/65bb5a0f10d4057ba7e5041f1b807923.webp?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e013d9338cba857b6373a6f.poster.avif?t=1773940416\" width=780 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e013d9338cba857b6373a6f.webm?t=1773940416\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2414270/extras/be1d2f824e